text: Shuqualak Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Mississippi. Shuqualak is a name derived from the Choctaw language purported to mean "beads". A variant name is "Shocoloc Creek". ==References== Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Kemper County, Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Noxubee County, Mississippi
title: Shuqualak Creek
